2016-05-08 18-00-00:
	Title: New stable release available!
	Author: Oliver Brakmann
	Content: We are happy to announce the latest stable release of OpenRA today!\n\nThe big stand-out features are under the hood this time, but there are still lots of things to look forward to in this release: targetable husks on refineries, a restart button, lots of bug fixes and many things more.\n\nHead over to http://openra.net to read the full announcement, and visit http://changelog.openra.net to see full changelog.\n\nWe hope you will enjoy this release! Download it now, and have fun!
